    'workflow.build.heading': 'Ship products that work,\nand keep working.',
    'workflow.build.body': "Good software rarely comes from clever abstractions. It comes from the dull work of clear boundaries, typed contracts, and tests that run. I build for whoever touches the code two years from now, not for today's excitement.",
