    'workflow.write.heading': 'Write to think.\nPublish to share.',
    'workflow.write.body': "Writing is how I find out what I actually understand. I publish long pieces on tooling, architecture decisions, and the tradeoffs that don't fit in a tweet. If one post saves you an afternoon of debugging, that's enough.",
